Advanced CSS Animations

Today's Focus: Keyframes, transitions, 3D transforms.
What I Learned:

@keyframes animations

CSS 3D transforms

Animation performance

Code:

css
/* 3D card flip */
.card {
    transition: transform 0.6s;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
}
.card.flipped {
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
}

